<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>휴일 근무 신청기</title>
  <meta property="og:title" content="휴일 근무 신청기">
  <meta property="og:description" content="휴일 근무 신청을 간편하게 관리하세요.">
  <meta property="og:image" content="https://i.imgur.com/4Q7W3Xl.png">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://tcw0182.github.io/holiday-work/">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <style>
    *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    body{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:100vh;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,sans-serif;background:#f1f2f6}
    .wrap{text-align:center;padding:30px}
    .icon{font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px}
    h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;color:#2d3436;margin-bottom:8px}
    p{font-size:14px;color:#636e72;margin-bottom:24px}
    .btn{display:inline-block;padding:12px 28px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0984e3,#6c5ce7);color:white;border-radius:24px;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none}
    .dots{display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:6px;margin-top:20px}
    .dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:#b2bec3;animation:bounce 1.2s infinite}
    .dot:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s}
    .dot:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.4s}
    @keyframes bounce{0%,80%,100%{transform:scale(0.8);opacity:0.5}40%{transform:scale(1.2);opacity:1}}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="icon">📅</div>
    <h2>휴일 근무 신청기</h2>
    <p>잠시 후 자동으로 이동합니다...</p>
    <a class="btn" href="① Apps Script URL"
       onclick="window.location.href=this.href">바로 이동하기</a>
    <div class="dots">
      <div class="dot"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div>
      <div class="dot"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script>
    setTimeout(function() {
      window.location.href = "https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbw8ZffJdVnf2s9rtMZyBy3r7bpEG_2_TRQ8-dVpV0YfIDWv_7ueZwVRc7dg9s6z8bQH/exec";
    }, 1500);
  </script>
</body>
</html>
